674. J Immunother Cancer. 2022 Nov;10(11):e005780. doi: 10.1136/jitc-2022-005780.

FRACTION-RCC: nivolumab plus ipilimumab for advanced renal cell carcinoma after 
progression on immuno-oncology therapy.

Choueiri TK(1)(2), Kluger H(3), George S(4), Tykodi SS(5)(6), Kuzel TM(7), 
Perets R(8)(9), Nair S(10), Procopio G(11), Carducci MA(12), Castonguay V(13), 
