675. Liver Int. 2023 Mar;43(3):639-648. doi: 10.1111/liv.15471. Epub 2022 Nov 15.

Disease burden in primary sclerosing cholangitis in the Netherlands: A long-term 
follow-up study.

van Munster KN(1), Mol B(1), Goet JC(2), van Munster SN(1), Weersma RK(3), de 
